        "subject": "LU-19123 utils: fix 'lfs project' on bad symlink v2",
        "message": "LU-19123 utils: fix 'lfs project' on bad symlink v2\n\nFix lfs_project_iterate() to also use lstat() instead of stat() to\nhandle broken symlinks.  Change the error messages for these cases to\nmake it more clear if someone is running the old version of this code\nand is reporting a problem.\n\nImprove sanity-quota test_64() to check this case.\n\nFixes: 588850bbeb (\"LU-19123 utils: allow 'lfs project' on bad symlinks\")\nFixes: 501e5b2c8a (\"LU-18027 lfs: lfs find handling special files\")\nTest-Parameters: trivial testlist=sanity-quota\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Iddd9553d7e3090dbff825e17bbda8541ff9c4ae5\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/61309\nReviewed-by: Rahul Bansal <rahulmay94@gmail.com>\nReviewed-by: Li Dongyang <dongyangli@ddn.com>\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
